  "id": "adv_bond_suz_01_03",
  "title": "成宮すず3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ～～～～～～。暇ですわ\n暇ですわ、暇ですわ、暇ですわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa~~~~~~. I'm so bored\nI'm so bored‚ I'm so bored‚ I'm so bored~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣と新しく買ったゲームをする約束をしていたのに\n急な仕事が入ってしまうなんて……はあ、暇ですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had promised to play the new game with Mei‚\nbut she got unexpected work… Haa‚ I'm so bored…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こころとすみれも出掛けたようですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like Kokoro and Sumire went out too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.4666659673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "なんで私のオフの日に限って寮に誰もいないんですの～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why is there no one in the dorm on my day off~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4666.666666600001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.333332634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！？　今玄関の方で音がした気が……\nもしかして……芽衣が帰って来たんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? I just heard a noise by the front door…\nPerhaps… Is Mei back!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.333332634,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6236.667365999999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.0166659673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣！　おかえりなさいまし！　遅いですわよ！\n早くゲームを……あら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei! Welcome back! You're late!\nLet's play the game… oh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0666659673,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.033332634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
