      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと、すず、なんなの？\nそんなに腕を強く引っ張らないでよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait a second‚ Suzu‚ what's going on?\nDon't pull my arm too hard",
        "id": ""
