      "text": "なんの話？　自分の部屋でゆっくりしたいんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about? I want to relax in my room…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2666669846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
